<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 00:34:12 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列希望立即释放人质；如果不完全停火，哈马斯不会让步</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-wants-hostages-freed-all-at-once-hamas-wont-budge-without-complete-cease-fire/0000018d-70c9-d971-a38f-71fbbfc50000</link><description>熟悉以色列和哈马斯谈判的消息人士称，两国距离达成协议还有很长的路要走，但双方都不反对达成一项协议。</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 22:48:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-wants-hostages-freed-all-at-once-hamas-wont-budge-without-complete-cease-fire/0000018d-70c9-d971-a38f-71fbbfc50000</guid></item><item><title>报告称，以色列军方对近东救济工程处指控的泄露感到惊讶</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/israeli-military-surprised-by-leak-of-unwra-accusations-report-says/0000018d-7089-d971-a38f-71bb73470000</link><description>《纽约时报》调查显示，1月18日，联合国驻加沙机构总干事会见了一名以色列外交官，该外交官透露了该机构员工参与袭击的情况，并在一周内将该信息发送给联合国和美国</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 20:46:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/israeli-military-surprised-by-leak-of-unwra-accusations-report-says/0000018d-7089-d971-a38f-71bb73470000</guid></item><item><title>“你应对 10 月 7 日大屠杀负责”：以色列各地数千人抗议内塔尼亚胡政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/.premium/you-are-responsible-for-the-oct-7-holocaust-thousands-protest-against-netanyahus-govt/0000018d-705a-d971-a38f-71fa927b0000</link><description>耶路撒冷的一名退休以色列国防军将军表示，本届政府未能就人质返回问题做出决定，未能就结束战争的政治愿景做出决定，也未能就 20 万难民返回家园做出决定。</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 20:31:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/.premium/you-are-responsible-for-the-oct-7-holocaust-thousands-protest-against-netanyahus-govt/0000018d-705a-d971-a38f-71fa927b0000</guid></item><item><title>数百人在哥伦比亚大学外抗议，谴责以色列是“新纳粹德国”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/.premium/denouncing-israel-as-the-new-nazi-germany-hundreds-protest-outside-columbia-university/0000018d-7091-dd6e-a98d-f4b3eca80000</link><description>反以色列抗议者高呼“起义万岁”和“定居者，定居者回家——巴勒斯坦是我们的”，沿着百老汇蔓延了几个街区，有时涌入街道并阻塞交通</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 20:15:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/.premium/denouncing-israel-as-the-new-nazi-germany-hundreds-protest-outside-columbia-university/0000018d-7091-dd6e-a98d-f4b3eca80000</guid></item><item><title>众议院共和党将推动向以色列提供超过 170 亿美元紧急援助的独立法案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/.premium/republicans-to-push-bill-providing-israel-with-17-6-billion-in-emergency-funding/0000018d-7084-dd6e-a98d-f4a6347e0000</link><description>该法案将于下周提出，正值参议院民主党人和共和党人就边境安全妥协问题进行紧张谈判，该妥协将为拜登的国家安全补充法案扫清道路，其中包括向以色列提供超过 140 亿美元的援助</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 20:02:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/.premium/republicans-to-push-bill-providing-israel-with-17-6-billion-in-emergency-funding/0000018d-7084-dd6e-a98d-f4a6347e0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙人报告哈马斯在以色列军队撤离的加沙北部地区恢复文官治理</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/gazans-report-resurgence-of-hamas-civilian-governance-north-gaza-vacated-by-idf/0000018d-6fc6-d4f1-a18d-fff640bb0000</link><description>哈马斯在加沙最大城市卷土重来的迹象突显了该组织的韧性，尽管自 10 月 7 日对以色列发动致命袭击并引发战争以来的四个月里，以色列发动了致命的空中和地面行动</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 17:48:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/gazans-report-resurgence-of-hamas-civilian-governance-north-gaza-vacated-by-idf/0000018d-6fc6-d4f1-a18d-fff640bb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列男子在自己拥有的餐厅被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-shot-dead-at-restaurant-he-owned/0000018d-6fd3-d971-a38f-7ff339a00000</link><description>警方表示，他们已对发生在以德鲁兹为主的北部城镇雅卡的涉嫌谋杀案展开调查</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 16:49:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-shot-dead-at-restaurant-he-owned/0000018d-6fd3-d971-a38f-7ff339a00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列监狱管理局前局长表示，极右翼部长本格维尔希望在该机构立足</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/former-head-of-israel-prison-service-says-ben-gvir-wanted-foothold-in-agency/0000018d-6f87-dd6e-a98d-ffa774c70000</link><description>前专员凯蒂·佩里表示，国家安全部长决定不延长她的任期，因为他希望有人为他工作</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 15:57:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/former-head-of-israel-prison-service-says-ben-gvir-wanted-foothold-in-agency/0000018d-6f87-dd6e-a98d-ffa774c70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列南部基布兹安全志愿者射杀因企图盗窃而被拘留的男子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-security-volunteer-shoots-dead-man-detained-for-attempted-theft/0000018d-6dfd-dd6e-a98d-fdfff6270000</link><description>死者的叔叔说，“[他]被枪杀是因为他是阿拉伯人” ■ 这名男子和另外两人翻过基布兹的栅栏后被拘留，据称他挣脱手铐并拔出一把刀后被枪杀</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 09:59:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-security-volunteer-shoots-dead-man-detained-for-attempted-theft/0000018d-6dfd-dd6e-a98d-fdfff6270000</guid></item><item><title>左派如何成为仇恨犹太人的政治</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-03/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/how-the-left-became-a-politics-of-hatred-against-jews/0000018d-6562-d7f7-adcf-6def4fe50000</link><description>如果之前还不清楚的话，那么全球左派与哈马斯的结盟就是其道德和智力破产的最终证据。现在是其他人必须推进启蒙价值观</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 05:34:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-03/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/how-the-left-became-a-politics-of-hatred-against-jews/0000018d-6562-d7f7-adcf-6def4fe50000</guid></item><item><title>在约旦河西岸这个“疯狂地带”，他们也向美国人开枪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-02-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-this-crazy-zone-in-the-west-bank-they-shoot-americans-too/0000018d-6d29-dd6e-a98d-fd2b53ee0000</link><description>以色列定居者和/或安全部队在西岸向一辆汽车开枪，杀死了一名年轻的巴勒斯坦美国人，他正准备在家乡新奥尔良开始学习工程学，并梦想在美国宇航局工作</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 04:36:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-02-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-this-crazy-zone-in-the-west-bank-they-shoot-americans-too/0000018d-6d29-dd6e-a98d-fd2b53ee0000</guid></item><item><title>Dalal Abu Amneh 是一位成功的歌手和神经科学家。以色列想要毁掉她的生活</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/dalal-abu-amneh-is-a-popular-singer-and-neuroscientist-israel-is-out-to-destroy-her-life/0000018d-6b82-d4f1-a18d-fff271bc0000</link><description>达拉尔·阿布·阿姆内的生活瞬间变成了地狱。这一切都始于她 10 月 7 日后发表的一篇模棱两可的帖子</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 04:10:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/dalal-abu-amneh-is-a-popular-singer-and-neuroscientist-israel-is-out-to-destroy-her-life/0000018d-6b82-d4f1-a18d-fff271bc0000</guid></item><item><title>美国和英国对也门胡塞武装目标进行一系列打击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article-live/u-s-strikes-over-85-pro-iranian-militia-targets-in-iraq-syria/0000018d-6cd8-dd6e-a98d-fcfa0ff90000</link><description>伊拉克称美国对伊朗支持的民兵组织的袭击造成 16 人死亡，其中包括平民 ■ 卡塔尔报告：前往开罗讨论人质协议的哈马斯代表团因“额外磋商”而推迟数天 ■ 中央司令部：美军击落了红线上空的几架胡塞武装无人机周五海上 ■ 以色列国防部长暗示加沙停火，称对真主党的袭击将继续</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 03:20:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article-live/u-s-strikes-over-85-pro-iranian-militia-targets-in-iraq-syria/0000018d-6cd8-dd6e-a98d-fcfa0ff90000</guid></item><item><title>美国严厉打击伊拉克和叙利亚民兵，对致命无人机袭击进行报复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/u-s-hits-hard-at-militias-in-iraq-and-syria-retaliating-for-fatal-drone-attack/0000018d-6c44-dd6e-a98d-fc6670590000</link><description>大规模的袭击击中了七个地点的超过 85 个目标。拜登：我们的回应从今天开始。它将在我们选择的时间和地点继续</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 00:23:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/u-s-hits-hard-at-militias-in-iraq-and-syria-retaliating-for-fatal-drone-attack/0000018d-6c44-dd6e-a98d-fc6670590000</guid></item><item><title>特鲁多总理表示，加拿大考虑对“极端主义”以色列约旦河西岸定居者实施制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-02/ty-article/canada-considers-sanctions-on-extremist-israeli-west-bank-settlers-pm-trudeau-says/0000018d-6b02-d971-a38f-7bb2dc580000</link><description>加拿大总理表示，约旦河西岸的暴力行为是绝对不可接受的，该地区的和平、稳定以及两国解决方案的道路都受到威胁。巴勒斯坦平民</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 18:33:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-02/ty-article/canada-considers-sanctions-on-extremist-israeli-west-bank-settlers-pm-trudeau-says/0000018d-6b02-d971-a38f-7bb2dc580000</guid></item><item><title>以色列安全内阁考虑与哈马斯达成为期142天的人质协议和停火协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-security-cabinet-mulls-proposed-142-day-hostage-deal-cease-fire-with-hamas/0000018d-6ac2-dd6e-a98d-fee220890000</link><description>一位消息人士告诉《国土报》，该计划提议在停火期间每天释放一名人质，但该计划遭到了内阁成员的严厉批评，他们反对延长停火期限和分阶段释放人质。极右翼部长本格维尔表示，这样的协议将为哈马斯提供氧气。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 17:43:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-security-cabinet-mulls-proposed-142-day-hostage-deal-cease-fire-with-hamas/0000018d-6ac2-dd6e-a98d-fee220890000</guid></item><item><title>管理战后加沙将需要许多为哈马斯工作的人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-02-02/ty-article/.premium/running-postwar-gaza-will-require-many-who-worked-for-hamas/0000018d-6a3e-d4f1-a18d-fe7e810d0000</link><description>除非以色列直接控制加沙，否则它将不得不允许巴勒斯坦权力机构雇用哈马斯雇用的数万名公务员。停火可能是让巴勒斯坦权力机构掌握权力的机会</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 15:27:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-02-02/ty-article/.premium/running-postwar-gaza-will-require-many-who-worked-for-hamas/0000018d-6a3e-d4f1-a18d-fe7e810d0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯表示正在研究以色列人质协议提案，致力于永久停火要求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-02/ty-article/hamas-says-its-studying-hostage-deal-proposal-committed-to-permanent-cease-fire-demand/0000018d-6a34-d971-a38f-7bb6bb380000</link><description>贝鲁特哈马斯高级官员奥萨马·哈姆丹表示，该组织要求释放数千名巴勒斯坦囚犯，并永久停火 — — 这一条件与埃及和以色列官员提出的多阶段提案相矛盾、卡塔尔和美国</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 15:14:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-02/ty-article/hamas-says-its-studying-hostage-deal-proposal-committed-to-permanent-cease-fire-demand/0000018d-6a34-d971-a38f-7bb6bb380000</guid></item><item><title>资料来源：沙特向以色列开放，绕过对巴勒斯坦国的约束性步骤，以争取美国国防协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-02/ty-article/saudis-open-to-israel-bypassing-binding-steps-for-palestinian-state-in-u-s-defense-bid/0000018d-6a2c-d971-a38f-7bbe1bcf0000</link><description>在美国领导的沙特阿拉伯和以色列之间的正常化努力因加沙战争陷入停滞后，官员们表示，利雅得不会坚持以色列采取具体步骤建立巴勒斯坦国，而是会接受对两国解决方案的政治承诺</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 15:09:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-02/ty-article/saudis-open-to-israel-bypassing-binding-steps-for-palestinian-state-in-u-s-defense-bid/0000018d-6a2c-d971-a38f-7bbe1bcf0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡是个破布？绝对地。在以色列，他并不孤单</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-02/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-a-rag-absolutely-and-in-israel-hes-not-alone/0000018d-698d-dd6e-a98d-fdafe6360000</link><description>用希伯来语的同义词来说，谁是聪明人？如果问 1000 万以色列人，简短的回答是“每个人”——当然，以色列政治中的白痴数量也在不断增加</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 13:07:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-02/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-a-rag-absolutely-and-in-israel-hes-not-alone/0000018d-698d-dd6e-a98d-fdafe6360000</guid></item></channel></rss>